window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mikhail's adventures continue. He's finding out ever more about this world, and the Empire in which he lives. But he's in for some surprises, still. They've tasked him with training the most hopeless students from the Department of Healing Arts. Perhaps this was meant to be a way of punishing Mikhail, but in the end, it's tough luck for the students.</p> <p>After all, look at who they got for a teacher! One thing's for sure, no way will these students end up as mediocre Healers!</p>"; 
